推"},{"pid":"c7f56788cd0022e84538b38ddb4bfaee020512b3","tid":1578361,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請大家盡量俾多D建議或公布一下各地行動資料<br />\n[統籌/文宣] 9.29 Global Anti Chinazi Rally<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahDQchU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahDQchU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網上：</span><br />\nTwitter,<br />\n每晚9點係twitter 開關於Chinazi既Tweet 再加以下hashtag<br />\n#929GlobalAntiChinaziRally<br />\n#AntiChinazi<br />\n個人建議集中2-3 Hashtag<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[集思廣益] 9.29 Global Anti Chinazi March, 推到全球70億人知<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575136</a></span><br />\n<br />\nReddit及各大Forum 開post宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港：</span><br />\n9.29 全球抗<span style=\"color: red;\">赤納粹</span>集會<br />\n由於9.28有民陣申請遊行，相信即使俾狗反對遊行亦會有大量手足上街，另外10.1亦係大日子上街，所以建議9.29只舉辦集會。<br />\n大家一齊討論下地點 時間等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人鏈包圍中国大使館活動<br />\n2019.09.29 14:00-16:00 EST<br />\n中共駐美國大使館</span></span><br />\n睇到有Post已經講左會係DC有人鏈包圍中国大使館<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">929美國DC有人鏈包圍中国大使館活動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575130</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">台灣：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">九二九台港大遊行：撐港．反極權<br />\n集合時間：2019年9月29日 15:00 集合地點：立法院旁濟南路<br />\n行動資訊：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/392770148103285/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F392770148103285%2F&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=35924bb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/392770148103285/</a><br />\n聯合聲明：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/taiwanwithhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftaiwanwithhongkong&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ad03fd3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/taiwanwithhongkong</a></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">台灣將舉辦 &quot;929大遊行&quot;撐香港 上百團體響應<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562513</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果可行的話，個人希望召喚到G20團隊協助眾籌及登報宣傳9.29既活動以配合10.1賀國慶既登報活動，黎個雙連擊<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=46125d81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n公海Group: <a href=\"http://t.me/joinchat/M_MebhKAE9TPr8Y_t2KKEw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FM_MebhKAE9TPr8Y_t2KKEw&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e8f44526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/joinchat/M_MebhKAE9TPr8Y_t2KKEw</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b0197e6350f959edf63d4b2da2fb199dc1d5687","tid":1578361,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32450e5708c3d9432819169f18752369d784446d","tid":1578361,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"隻馬都罷工?"},{"pid":"3da05a5c08337e0d1033aa2994589f8f8dbdce8b","tid":1578361,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a462cc62c207c49482e1de48d2232399d22b324","tid":1578361,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c83b6e8b0edf97f003a7038910284e1d5ef6a295","tid":1578361,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"